TEXT(CAPA_EV (<<'END_OF_TEXT'));
What is the magnitude of the vector \{ CAPA_tex( '/*\vec a/*'  , 'a'  )  \} + \{ CAPA_tex( '/*\vec b/*'  , 'b'  )  \}?
END_OF_TEXT

